Package org.soulwing.jdbc.logger

Logging support

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JdbcLogger
    A simplified log writer interface for logging SQL statements and bound parameter values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JclLogger
    A JdbcLogger that delegates to a Commons Logging logger.
    JuliLogger
    A JdbcLogger that delegates to Logger.
    NullLogger
    A singleton JdbcLogger that does nothing.
    PrintWriterLogger
    A JdbcLogger that delegates to a print stream or print writer.

    Package org.soulwing.jdbc.logger Description

    Logging support

    This package provides various implementations of the JdbcLogger interface to allow SQL statements and bound parameter values to be conveniently logged.
